pageContext.claim: “You've got a tremendous number of dishonest media people, like, I have never seen in my life before. They write things that they know are wrong. They write -- if you watched for the last three years, think of it, and then, they get Pulitzer Prizes, but it turned out to be all wrong.”
pageContext.analysis: The Washington Post and New York Times won Pulitzers for writing articles on Trump and his administration that were not wrong.
